{"title":"Spring boot 2.X启动报错：Specified key was too long; max key length is 1000 bytes","date":"2018-12-03T06:57:37.000Z","slug":"Spring-boot-2-X启动报错：Specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-1000-bytes","comments":true,"tags":["Spring Boot"],"updated":"2019-05-11T17:10:12.495Z","content":"<h2 id=\"原因\">原因<a href=\"post/Spring-boot-2-X启动报错：Specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-1000-bytes#原因\"></a></h2><p>Spring boot 2.x默认使用的mysql 引擎为myisam，但是Spring boot2.0之前使用的是InnoDB，Spring boot2.0之后默认使用的是myisam引擎。然后在新建表的时候。就出这个错了</p>\n<h2 id=\"解决\">解决<a href=\"post/Spring-boot-2-X启动报错：Specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-1000-bytes#解决\"></a></h2><p>在配置文件中加如下配置:<br><figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">spring:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    jpa:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">      database-platform:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"comment\"># spring boot 2.0 的坑， spring boot2.+后默认使用的是MyISAM引擎</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL5InnoDBDialect</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Hadoop伪分布式搭建","slug":"Hadoop伪分布式搭建"},"next":{"title":"docker将本地目录挂载到容器","slug":"docker将本地目录挂载到容器"},"link":"http://wooo.io/post/Spring-boot-2-X启动报错：Specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-1000-bytes/","toc":[{"title":"原因","id":"原因","index":"1"},{"title":"解决","id":"解决","index":"2"}]}